를 선택하면 인스턴스타입을 선택하는화면이 없어진다. 스케일업/다운이 사용량따라 자동으로 조절되기때문               스케일링 시에는 CloudWatch에 표시됨     ACU: Aurora Capacity Unit           2GB메모리에 맞는 사양으로 구성됨      과금 시 ACU단위로 과금됨               읽기 성능확장 (master node) 기능에서 읽기/쓰기확장 (multi master) 기능 가능해짐           샤딩에서 멀티마스터로 사용가능               분산 원장을 통한 Conflict해결           블로그 페이지 참조.      쿼럼 획득???                      Aurora Parallel Query         스토리지를 활용한 쿼리 프로세싱 병렬화     스토리지 데이터처리라서 네트워크 트래픽 시간을 줄임     성능           약5배~ 25배 빠름               사용           Set session aurora_pq={'on'/'off'}               모니터링           Show global status               평가판신청 사용 가능                   ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:12px;top:170px;width:564px\">\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Aurora Serverless</h2>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC778;&#xC2A4;&#xD134;&#xC2A4;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> &#xC0DD;&#xC131; &#xD6C4; &#xCCAB; &#xC694;&#xCCAD; &#xC2DC;&#xC5D0; &#xD504;&#xB85C;&#xBE44;&#xC800;&#xB2DD;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC5B4;&#xD50C;&#xB9AC;&#xCF00;&#xC774;&#xC158;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBD80;&#xD558;&#xB7C9;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBAA8;&#xB2C8;&#xD130;&#xB9C1;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBAA8;&#xB2C8;&#xD130;&#xB9C1;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xC790;&#xB3D9;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xC2A4;&#xCF00;&#xC77C; &#xC5C5;/&#xB2E4;&#xC6B4;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC778;&#xC2A4;&#xD134;&#xC2A4;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0DD;&#xC131;&#xD654;&#xBA74;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\">..</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\">DB engine configuration<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;</span> serverless<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB97C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC120;&#xD0DD;&#xD558;&#xBA74;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC778;&#xC2A4;&#xD134;&#xC2A4;&#xD0C0;&#xC785;&#xC744;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC120;&#xD0DD;&#xD558;&#xB294;&#xD654;&#xBA74;&#xC774;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC5C6;&#xC5B4;&#xC9C4;&#xB2E4;</span>. <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC2A4;&#xCF00;&#xC77C;&#xC5C5;</span>/<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB2E4;&#xC6B4;&#xC774;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xB7C9;&#xB530;&#xB77C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC790;&#xB3D9;&#xC73C;&#xB85C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC870;&#xC808;&#xB418;&#xAE30;&#xB54C;&#xBB38;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC2A4;&#xCF00;&#xC77C;&#xB9C1; &#xC2DC;&#xC5D0;&#xB294; CloudWatch&#xC5D0; &#xD45C;&#xC2DC;&#xB428;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">ACU: Aurora Capacity Unit</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">2GB&#xBA54;&#xBAA8;&#xB9AC;&#xC5D0; &#xB9DE;&#xB294; &#xC0AC;&#xC591;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xAD6C;&#xC131;&#xB428;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xACFC;&#xAE08; &#xC2DC; ACU&#xB2E8;&#xC704;&#xB85C; &#xACFC;&#xAE08;&#xB428;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC77D;&#xAE30; &#xC131;&#xB2A5;&#xD655;&#xC7A5; (master node) &#xAE30;&#xB2A5;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xC77D;&#xAE30;/&#xC4F0;&#xAE30;&#xD655;&#xC7A5; (multi master) &#xAE30;&#xB2A5; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD574;&#xC9D0;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0E4;&#xB529;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xBA40;&#xD2F0;&#xB9C8;&#xC2A4;&#xD130;&#xB85C; &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBD84;&#xC0B0; &#xC6D0;&#xC7A5;&#xC744; &#xD1B5;&#xD55C; Conflict&#xD574;&#xACB0;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBE14;&#xB85C;&#xADF8; &#xD398;&#xC774;&#xC9C0; &#xCC38;&#xC870;.</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xCFFC;&#xB7FC; &#xD68D;&#xB4DD;???</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Aurora Parallel Query</h2>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC2A4;&#xD1A0;&#xB9AC;&#xC9C0;&#xB97C; &#xD65C;&#xC6A9;&#xD55C; &#xCFFC;&#xB9AC; &#xD504;&#xB85C;&#xC138;&#xC2F1; &#xBCD1;&#xB82C;&#xD654;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC2A4;&#xD1A0;&#xB9AC;&#xC9C0; &#xB370;&#xC774;&#xD130;&#xCC98;&#xB9AC;&#xB77C;&#xC11C; &#xB124;&#xD2B8;&#xC6CC;&#xD06C; &#xD2B8;&#xB798;&#xD53D; &#xC2DC;&#xAC04;&#xC744; &#xC904;&#xC784;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC131;&#xB2A5;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC57D;5&#xBC30;~ 25&#xBC30; &#xBE60;&#xB984;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Set session aurora_pq={&apos;on&apos;/&apos;off&apos;}</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBAA8;&#xB2C8;&#xD130;&#xB9C1;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle;font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Show global status</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD3C9;&#xAC00;&#xD310;&#xC2E0;&#xCCAD; &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}